title: My Dent Guy Offers Convenient In-Shop and Mobile Paintless Dent Repair Services in Naples, FL | News | decaturdailydemocrat.com
text: Naples, FL - My Dent Guy, a leading provider of high-quality paintless dent repair services , is pleased to announce its convenient in-shop and mobile services in Naples, FL. With a commitment to exceptional customer service, My Dent Guy is revolutionizing the dent repair industry by offering efficient and cost-effective solutions for vehicles of all makes and models. Paintless dent repair (PDR) is a specialized technique that allows for the removal of dents, dings, and hail damage without the need for traditional bodywork, sanding, or repainting. With over 11 years of experience, My Dent Guy’s PDR expertise has perfected this method, ensuring that customers receive outstanding results with minimal disruption to their daily lives. Convenience is a top priority for My Dent Guy. Understanding that time is valuable, the company offers both in-shop and mobile services to accommodate its customers' busy schedules. Their state-of-the-art facility in Naples, FL, is equipped with cutting-edge tools and equipment, enabling their technicians to handle any dent repair job, from minor door dings to more extensive damage. Customers can drop off their vehicles at the shop, and the skilled technician at My Dent Guy will promptly restore them to their original condition. For those unable to visit the shop, My Dent Guy's mobile service brings the expertise directly to the customer's location. Whether at home, work, or even during a shopping trip, customers can conveniently schedule an appointment, and My Dent Guy's technician will arrive fully equipped to tackle the dent repair on-site. This hassle-free service saves customers time and eliminates the need for multiple trips to the shop. "We understand the stress and inconvenience that dents and dings can cause for vehicle owners," said Mark Tucker, of My Dent Guy. "That's why we are committed to providing our customers in Naples, FL, with exceptional paintless dent repair services that are convenient and affordable. Whether they choose to visit our shop or utilize our mobile service, we guarantee outstanding results and a seamless experience." My Dent Guy's commitment to customer satisfaction extends beyond their repair services. They offer free estimates and competitive pricing, to make the process as smooth as possible. Mark Tucker is dedicated to delivering unparalleled workmanship and attention to detail, ensuring that every customer is thrilled with the results. About My Dent Guy My Dent Guy is a leading provider of paintless dent repair services in Naples, FL. My Dent Guy offers convenient in-shop and mobile services for vehicles of all makes and models. His expertise utilizes state-of-the-art techniques and tools to provide efficient and cost-effective dent repairs, saving customers time and money. For more information or to schedule an appointment, visit www.callmydentguy.com or call 239-564-3368. title: Площадь лесных пожаров Бурятии превысила 10 тысяч гектаров | Regional News | Seldon News
text: За прошедшие сутки в Бурятии обнаружено 12 возгораний лесного фонда восьми районах республики, общая площадь пожаров достигла 10,5 тысячи гектаров. По оперативным данным Агентства лесного хозяйства Бурятии, на утро 8 мая в республике действует 21 лесной пожар, в том числе в Баунтовском, Джидинском, Еравнинском и Кяхтинском районах. "Угрозы населённым пунктам нет, пожары низкой интенсивности", – уточнили в Агентстве. К тушению огня привлечены 388 человек и 92 единицы техники, которым удалось ликвидировать восемь очагов пожаров. El presidente de Uruguay acusa a la "dictadura" de Maduro de confirmar el "fraude" electoral
cope.es
El presidente de Uruguay, Luis Lacalle Pou, ha afirmado que la sentencia del TSJ que avala la victoria de Nicolás Maduro viene a servir a la "dictadura" para confirmar el "fraude", por lo que ha llamado a seguir apoyando las reivindicaciones opositoras. "El régimen de Maduro confirma lo que la comunidad internacional viene denunciando: el fraude", afirmó Lacalle Pou que hay "una dictadura que cierra todas las puertas a una vida institucional y democrática de su pueblo". "No debemos callar ni cesar en defensa de la causa venezolana" ha recalcado
